<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880216-0138 </DOCNO><HL> Mayfair Industries Buy-Back </HL><SO> </SO><CO> MAYF </CO><IN> BBK </IN><DATELINE> NEW YORK  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Mayfair Industries Inc. said directors authorized the company to buy back as many as 150,000 of its common shares in the open market.    The apparel company said that it considers its stock &quot;highly undervalued&quot; at current prices. The company has 3.7 million common shares outstanding. The shares closed Friday at $5.50, up 50 cents, in over-the-counter trading. </TEXT></DOC>